import React from 'react';
import { Box, VStack, HStack, Text, Link, Heading, Divider, Container, Flex } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Box bg="white" borderBottom="1px" borderColor="gray.200" py={4}>
        <Container maxW="container.xl">
          <HStack justifyContent="space-between">
            <Text fontSize="2xl" fontWeight="bold">Dashboard</Text>
            <HStack spacing={4}>
              <Link href="#">Home</Link>
              <Link href="#">Profile</Link>
              <Link href="#">Messages</Link>
              <Link href="#">Settings</Link>
              <Link href="#">Logout</Link>
            </HStack>
          </HStack>
        </Container>
      </Box>
      <Container maxW="container.xl" mt={4}>
        <Flex>
          <VStack as="aside" width="250px" spacing={4} align="stretch" borderRight="1px" borderColor="gray.200" pr={4}>
            <Text fontWeight="bold">Navigation</Text>
            <Link href="#">Dashboard</Link>
            <Link href="#">My Sessions</Link>
            <Link href="#">Resources</Link>
            <Link href="#">Feedback</Link>
            <Link href="#">Settings</Link>
          </VStack>
          <VStack flex={1} spacing={4} align="stretch" pl={4}>
            <Box bg="white" p={6} borderRadius="md" boxShadow="sm">
              <Heading as="h1" size="lg" mb={4}>Welcome to the Dashboard!</Heading>
              <Divider />
              <Box mt={4}>
                <Heading as="h2" size="md" mb={2}>Upcoming Sessions</Heading>
                <Box p={4} borderWidth="1px" borderRadius="md" mb={2}>
                  <Heading as="h3" size="sm">Session Title</Heading>
                  <Text>Date: May 28, 2024</Text>
                  <Text>Time: 10:00 AM - 11:00 AM</Text>
                </Box>
                <Box p={4} borderWidth="1px" borderRadius="md">
                  <Heading as="h3" size="sm">Session Title</Heading>
                  <Text>Date: May 29, 2024</Text>
                  <Text>Time: 2:00 PM - 3:00 PM</Text>
                </Box>
              </Box>
              <Box mt={4}>
                <Heading as="h2" size="md" mb={2}>Resources</Heading>
                <VStack align="start">
                  <Link href="#">Resource 1</Link>
                  <Link href="#">Resource 2</Link>
                  <Link href="#">Resource 3</Link>
                </VStack>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </VStack>
        </Flex>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default App;
